verbose_text: Lastly, although Annexin-V + CD8 T cells increased ~ 2.5 fold in the CNS of JHMV infected WT mice following CD4 T cell depletion and IL-21 is known to promote CD8 T cell survival, IL-21R deficiency did not alter frequencies of CNS derived Annexin-V + CD8 T cells.
evidence: CD8 T cells increased ~ 2.5 fold in the CNS
